title: Net Cribbage 5.4 For PC
description:
ABOUT THIS GAME:

Play Cribbage with your friends and PC. Our Net Cribbage gives
you a chance to play Six Card Cribbage with computer bots or
live opponents by the Internet or LAN. It is also possible to
play simultaneously on two tables easily switching from game to
game. For each table you can use your own preferences; change
information window settings; select cards and cloth views.
